armenia
yerevan
related_items.title: Erewani hatakagitsě 1920 tʻ.
description: General-content city street map hand col. to show generalized land use. Note printed on title label affixed to cover: A First Republic era map of Yerevan before Tamanian's master plan (1924). Originally printed on 2 sheets (now conjoined). Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. LC copy mounted under clear mylar sheet on paper backing within paperboard frame. LC copy imperfect: Fragile, brittle, fold-lined, missing small sections of margins along sheet edges. LC copy accompanied by small-scale reverse-image photocopy of principal map (in mylar envelope affixed to inside of top cover). Includes index to points of interest.
other_title: Plan of Yerevan 1920 / drawn by M. Astvadzaturean
